{"tid":59854,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日模美舞偕男模挑戰12連拍擺POSE　突然「褲子掉了」!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2016-12-30T04:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T05:09:52.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c366f8e0699112bdf3696180646c6a1ced07393","tid":59854,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2243/d2243719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2243%2Fd2243719.jpg&h=a3e76977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲模特兒美舞分享工作影片，和男模挑戰12連拍，突然男方褲子掉了！<br />\n<br />\n日本模特兒美舞近日分享一則短片爆紅！她和男模在攝影棚拍照，配合攝影師速按快門，不間斷擺出各種POSE，就在達成12連拍的時候，男方的褲子突然掉下來啦！<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2015/12/20151202_EN_%E6%9C%B1%E5%8D%83%E9%9B%AA_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2015%2F12%2F20151202_EN_%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%258D%2583%25E9%259B%25AA_02.jpg&h=5587f030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片中，男模和美舞拍照進行到一半時改戴起墨鏡，繼續擺出2到3個姿勢後，突然褲子滑到膝蓋，露出白色內褲。而他遇到這情況，第一時間居然不是把褲子拉上來，而是維持拍照姿勢，依舊面無表情，身旁的工作人員則趕緊上前幫忙拉上褲子，但是沒多久褲子又掉了！等到褲子再度被拉回腰際後，又繼續展開連拍動作，彷彿剛剛什麼事情都沒有發生！<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2243/d2243720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2243%2Fd2243720.jpg&h=85254e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲模特兒美舞分享工作影片，和男模挑戰12連拍，突然男方褲子掉了！<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2243/d2243721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2243%2Fd2243721.jpg&h=498f4e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲工作人員上前幫忙穿褲子，沒想到褲子又滑下去了！<br />\n<br />\n美舞事後上傳影片，留言「這突發狀況是怎麼搞的？明明超爆笑卻拼命忍，笑笑笑笑！」網友跟著留言「太爆笑」，同時狂讚「為什麼沒人笑場」、「這真是專業！」還有人稱讚男模身材好，「我看完想要加油減肥了。」影片瞬間造成網路瘋傳。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nl_GWwexZeY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fnl_GWwexZeY&d=yCTaMrpfOZ6CYUu1fmQGLwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2ab3987e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nl_GWwexZeY</a>"},{"pid":"07724ce15e60438de8e5c018a767889089fa6f12","tid":59854,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戇鳩<br />\n點解唔自己拉返條褲？"},{"pid":"269dcb1574778dab4c2e8ee363b20d739daf0bf3","tid":59854,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"條女幾正"},{"pid":"63f39f248652b9d971cebdd3ed59ee7a265e37b4","tid":59854,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}